title: MJ Fresh: Talks Toxic Exes, Custody Battles and Why She Won't Be Silenced
itunes:title: MJ Fresh: Talks Toxic Exes, Custody Battles and Why She Won't Be Silenced
description:
MJ Fresh is back and better than ever to give us a life update, and to call out some vultures in the industry. She and Bunnie talk about toxic exes and bad breakups, what life is like now that her career has skyrocketed, and how she got the confidence to speak up for herself without caring what anyone else thinks.
